How to install pyttsx3:
-Open the Command Prompt (cmd.exe) on your computer. You can do so by opening the "Start" menu and searching up "cmd"
-Type in "pip install pyttsx3"

How to install pygame:
-Open the Command Prompt.
-Type in "pip install pygame"

Tkinter does not need to be manually installed as it is already included in the Python application.

See video tutorial if more help is needed.
